name: Biden speech
summary: Biden has officially withdrawn from the 2024 presidential race, and his first Oval Office address since making this decision has been met with mixed reactions. Some media outlets, such as The Associated Press, have highlighted Trump's immediate targeting of Harris as a political strategy. Others, like BBC.com, have criticized Biden for avoiding difficult truths in his speech. Al Jazeera English provides key takeaways from the address, while NBC News reports on Tucker Carlson's criticism of the Biden administration during the RNC speech. Several news sources, including ABC News, Axios, NBC Chicago, and The New York Times, offer guidance on how and when to tune in to Biden's address. Reuters reports on Biden's passing of the torch to defend democracy, while MSNBC's Jen Psaki analyzes the historic significance of Biden's speech in the Oval Office.

name: USA basketball
summary: The United States women's basketball team defeated Germany in an exhibition match as part of the USA Basketball Showcase in London. Team USA is preparing for the 2024 Paris Olympics, and the latest scores and updates are available on ESPN. NBC Los Angeles provides a historical overview of Team USA's basketball jerseys throughout Olympic history. CBS Sports outlines the team's schedule and roster for the 2024 Olympics, including star players like LeBron James and Stephen Curry. Despite a close call, Team USA men's basketball narrowly defeated South Sudan in a tune-up game for the Paris Olympics. USA TODAY highlights the key moments from the exhibition showcase, where the US team narrowly avoided an upset against South Sudan. NBA.com provides five takeaways from the USA Basketball Showcase, analyzing the team's performance and prospects. CNN reports on LeBron James leading Team USA to a 92-88 victory over Germany, while The Associated Press details James' game-winning shot in a 101-100 triumph against South Sudan. CBS News provides information on the team's upcoming schedule and the details of the Olympics showcases.
